{"TopicId":156888,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Can\u0026#039;t make images links on forums","CreatedByName":"minepagan","CreatedById":132643,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T23:30:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"minepagan","CreatedById":132643,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T23:30:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(not really sure where to post this)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seem to be having an issue making an image into a link. Now, if you\u0027d click on either of the images in my signature you\u0027d see that they are links, and\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ethey\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0work. But, for some reason, I am unable to add an image to a post and then make it a link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs a matter of fact, the \u0022Link\u0022 button does\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eabsolutely nothing\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0if I have an image highlighted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny help would be appreciated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Slam_Jones","CreatedById":125101,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T23:35:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLog In (top right corner), then click your name and go to \u0027Images\u0027\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022t2DehaQ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/t2DehaQ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022z2PqjXm.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/z2PqjXm.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Vgzf5W3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Vgzf5W3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Copy and Paste the BBCode link into your post for it to work!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-23T23:41:58Z\u0022 title=\u002202/23/2017 11:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u00